<concept id="concept_E8D43EB4494E41D2AB42D4A89396D1AB"
                    xml:lang="en-us">
    <title>HTTPS Support</title>
    <conbody>
        <section>
            <p>By default, the <ph conref="../product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                    /> components use the HTTP protocol for communication. For a more secure connection, <ph
                    conref="../product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                    /> can be configured to use the HTTPS protocol. If you want to use the HTTPS protocol, contact your <ph
                    conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                /> support for further information.</p>
        </section>
    </conbody>
</concept>
